overage collection (JaCoCo) and dynamic-access reporting per coordinate.\ndocs/FUNCTIONAL_SPEC.md:74:- `latest/badges.json` — badges shown in the README (libraries supported, tested versions, dynamic-access coverage, tested LOC).\ndocs/FUNCTIONAL_SPEC.md:84:1. **Add new library support** — generate a JUnit test suite, scaffold metadata, iterate until JVM-mode tests pass and dynamic-access metadata is collected.\ndocs/FUNCTIONAL_SPEC.md:87:4. **Improve coverage** of already-supported libraries by targeting uncovered dynamic-access call sites.\ndocs/DEVELOPING.md:329:  Output: `metadata/<group>/<artifact>/<version>/test/build/reports/dynamic-access/dynamic-access-coverage.json`\ntests/tck-build-logic/src/test/java/org/graalvm/internal/tck/stats/LibraryStatsSupportTests.java:36:        Path dynamicAccessDir = tempDir.resolve(\"dynamic-access\");\ntests/tck-build-logic/src/test/java/org/graalvm/internal/tck/stats/LibraryStatsSupportTests.java:114:        Path missingDynamicAccessDir = tempDir.resolve(\"dynamic-access-missing\");\ntests/tck-build-logic/src/test/java/org/graalvm/internal/tck/stats/LibraryStatsSupportTests.java:150:                tempDir.resolve(\"dynamic-access-missing\"),\ntests/tck-build-logic/src/test/java/org/graalvm/internal/tck/stats/LibraryStatsSupportTests.java:198:        Path dynamicAccessDir = tempDir.resolve(\"dynamic-access\");\ntests/tck-build-logic/src/test/java/org/graalvm/internal/tck/stats/LibraryStatsSupportTests.java:300:        Path dynamicAccessDir = tempDir.resolve(\"dynamic-access\");\ntests/tck-build-logic/src/test/java/org/graalvm/internal/tck/stats/LibraryStatsSupportTests.java:384:        Path missingDynamicAccessDir = tempDir.resolve(\"dynamic-access-missing\");\ntests/tck-build-logic/src/test/java/org/graalvm/internal/tck/stats/LibraryStatsSupportTests.java:420:                tempDir.resolve(\"dynamic-access-missing\"),\ntests/tck-build-logic/src/test/java/org/graalvm/internal/tck/harness/tasks/PopulateArtifactURLsTests.jav